list.abstract: Independent（英[ˌɪndɪˈpendənt]，美[ˌɪndɪˈpendənt]），英语单词，作形容词用，为自主的；独立的；不依赖权威的。作名词用，为独立自主者；独立团体；无党派人士。短语搭配有independent suspension（独立悬挂），例句为“I grow up to be completely independent.（我长大后完全独立。）” Independent作形容词时，近义词有alone、free、isolated等，相关反义词有dependent，名词形式为independence、independency。
《INDEPENDENT》是由李双周和李少峰作词，dAice作曲，ATF演唱的歌曲，收录于同名专辑《INDEPENDENT》，发行于2016年3月26日。

yingyinNormal.en: In fact, monetary policy is set by an independent Federal Reserve System, or The Fed, made up of 12 regional banks in major cities around the country.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上，货币政策是由独立的联邦准备系统制定，也就是联准会，其下有十二家区域银行散布在美国的各大都市。

yingyinNormal.en: Look at us, Riles, two young, independent women taking their own road, making their own way with their guts and their brains. Needing nothing from nobody from this moment on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧瞧我们，小莱，两个年轻、独立的女人走上属于自己的道路，利用自己的胆量和智慧一路往前闯。从此不需要任何人的任何帮助！

yingyinNormal.en: Because the bank works. It's independent. It pays for itself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为这家银行的工作卓有成效，而且是独立运行，自负盈亏。

yingyinNormal.en: You work for the NSA? I'm an independent contractor. For the NSA? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是国家安全局的雇员？我是独立合约员工。为国家安全局工作吗？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: The Irish gig guy? His legs flail about as if independent of his body.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个跳舞的爱尔兰人？他那双脚跳舞时，好像跟身体分离了一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't listen to your mother. You are independent and you always have been.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别听你妈乱讲话，你都很独立，一直都是。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I didn't realize how easy we have it now that Lily's so independent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，我之前都没意识到现在莉莉这么大了，我们过得有多舒坦。

yingyinNormal.en: Independent experts said it would grow our economy, and shrink our deficits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 独立专家说这会促进我们的经济增长，能够减少我们的赤字。

yingyinNormal.en: Del, I'll be frank. This is bad science. We need an independent test using top-of-the-line DNA sequencers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 戴尔，直说吧，这是邪恶科学，我们需要独立检测用最先进的DNA测序仪。

yingyinNormal.en: Mitchell, he's not going to accept it. It's just a gesture. We do it so we feel more independent. Just do it. Do it!
yingyinNormal.zh: 米奇尔，他不会收的，这只是一个姿态，我们这么做只是想显得更独立，听我的，把钱还给他。

yingyinNormal.en: And so began our adventure. An independent international intelligence agency operating at the highest level of discretion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的冒险就这样开始了。一个拥有最高度自由裁判权的独立国际情报机构。

yingyinNormal.en: No, not really. It's an independent film, you know? So we don't have a real big budget. I figured I'd just stay in your room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不算是，这是独立制片的电影，没有大预算，我想我住你房间好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Is that because you are an independent contractor engaged by Lockhart/Gardner, and technically not an employee of the firm? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是因为你是和洛&加律所签约的独立合同人，严格说来并非律所雇员，对吗？对。

yingyinNormal.en: They're independent markets. They're not always correlated. I know it sounds odd, but these are very complicated products. They are correlated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们属于独立市场，并不是总是相关的，我知道这听起来很奇怪，但这本来就是非常复杂的产品。它们是互相关联的。

yingyinNormal.en: If you'd rather cook at home, you can shop at over 3,000 supermarket chains and hundreds of thousands of independent grocery stores in the U.S..
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你更喜欢在家自己做饭，在美国，你能在超过3000家连锁超市以及成百上千家杂货店里，买到需要的食材。

yingyinNormal.en: In the past, I would have always wanted to do what I, myself, thought was best. But now I sought out the strongest independent thinkers I could find. I still do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在过去我总想做自己认为最好的事。现在我寻找能找到的最强独立思考者。 我一直这么做。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? I'm with Leonard, this isn't cool. Thank you. I disagree. Penny is a strong, independent woman. The more you try to control her, the more she'll push back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我支持莱纳德？这样是不对的。谢谢。我不同意。佩妮是一个独立而坚强的新女性。你越想掌控她，她反抗越强烈。

yingyinNormal.en: What you choose to do with these principles is up to you. You have to be an independent thinker, because only you can develop your own principles based on your own values.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要自己选择怎么看待这些法则。要有独立思考的能力，因为只有你能基于自己的价值观发展自己的法则。
